text: Naveen is a Data Scientist with 4+ years of experience in AI-driven solutions, automation, and scalable data pipelines. Expert in Python, AWS, TensorFlow, SQL, and Big Data.
Data Scientist at Corp 2 Corp Inc (Aug 2024 – Present). Integrated RASA chatbot, automated AWS pipelines. Programmer Analyst at Cognizant (2021–2022): Optimized ETL workflows, led CRM automation.
Python, TensorFlow, PyTorch, SQL, AWS (S3, Lambda, DynamoDB), Apache Airflow, Spark, Big Data, Generative AI, Docker, RASA.
MSc in Data Science (Stevens Institute, 2024). BTech in Electronics & Communication Engineering (GITAM University, 2021).
Investo: Stock prediction app using AWS. Ask PDF: AI-powered document search system. TypeSQL: Text-to-SQL generator.
AI & Data Pioneer Award (Corp 2 Corp Inc, 2025) for boosting revenue by 20%. Cognizant Bronze Cheers Award (2022) for CRM workflow automation.
